vp (1.9) unstable; urgency=medium

  * SDL2 port and CMake build alongside autotools.
  * Optional https via OpenSSL (certificate verification, -k), IPv6, HTTP
    redirect following, correct HTTP/1.1 framing, -K to keep downloads.
  * Arbitrary pan and zoom, on-screen filename display, oversized-image
    handling.
  * Security hardening of the download path; dropped unimplemented FTP.

